channel.title: Commands
channel.description: Hi i have a PI source im in need of a couple commands 1. ::xteletome 2. ::xteleto 3. ::setlevel (ex: ::setlevel 22 99 Imperialist) (22 = skill number 99= level imperialist = the name of the character) Thank you!

item.title: Commands
item.dc:creator: @imsuperman05 imsuperman05
item.description:
@imsuperman05 wrote:

[quote=“xXxSkillerxXx, post:1, topic:422620”]Hi i have a PI source im in need of a couple commands

  1. ::xteletome
  2. ::xteleto
  3. ::setlevel (ex: ::setlevel 22 99 Imperialist)
    (22 = skill number 99= level imperialist = the name of the character)
    Thank you![/quote]

[code=java]
if(playerCommand.startsWith(“xteletome”)) {
String otherPerson = playerCommand.subString(11);
for(int j = 0; j < PlayerHandler.players.length; j++) {
Client Other = (Client) PlayerHandler.players[j];
if(Other == null || c == null)
return;
if(Other.playerName.equalsIgnoreCase(otherPerson)) {
Other.getPA().movePlayer(c.absX, c.absY, c.heightLevel);
}
}
}

if(playerCommand.startsWith(“xteleto”)) {
String otherPerson = playerCommand.subString(9);
for(int j = 0; j < PlayerHandler.players.length; j++) {
Client Other = (Client) PlayerHandler.players[j];
if(Other == null || c == null)
return;
if(Other.playerName.equalsIgnoreCase(otherPerson)) {
c.getPA().movePlayer(Other.absX, Other.absY, c.heightLevel);
}
}
}[/code]
